snippet.title: Hoppy Woods - 2D Platformer Game Made with Godot
snippet.description:
This is the finished build of my first published game that's made with the Godot engine!

You can play it on Itch.io here: https://charlexmachina.itch.io/hoppy-woods

You can also find its source code here: https://github.com/OldManCharles/Hoppy-Woods
